transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra Quinn speaking, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes sir, I'd like to cancel my prescription.

Speaker 1: Okay, let me pull up your account. Is your name Jeff?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Alrighty Jeff, I do see you are VIP with this here. Do you mind if I ask why you're cancelling your Viagra today?

Speaker 2: I don't need it any more longer.

Speaker 1: Okay, you can always order this as needed if you're getting it too fast.

Speaker 2: I just wish to cancel it right now.

Speaker 1: Okay, yeah, order as needed means you wouldn't get it again until you call us, so we can give you plenty of time.

Speaker 2: Okay, yeah, we can do that.

Speaker 1: Alright, so what we do is just keep your prescription open for the next five months and you'll have to call us for your next one, okay?

Speaker 2: Okay, that'll be fine.

Speaker 1: Alrighty, we'll do that for you now sir.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: You're welcome. You have a good day.

Speaker 2: You too, bye.
